name: market group for inorganic potassium fertiliser, as K2O | inorganic potassium fertiliser, as K2O | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/22747/documentation

This is a market group that aggregates 'inorganic potassium fertiliser, as K2O' for a strictly agricultural use as fertiliser in the given geography. The purpose of this dataset is to group a set of markets into larger, geographically relevant datasets.;Market groups are created for convenience and ease of use. They only group other markets and/or market groups contained within their geography.;Losses and relevant exchanges (transport, transport infrastructure, etc.) are not included in this dataset. They are present in the contained markets.  ;copy Q

This activity starts at the gate of markets that deliver ''inorganic potassium fertiliser, as K2O'' in geographies contained within the geography of this dataset.

This activity ends with the supply of 1 kg of ''inorganic potassium fertiliser, as K2O'' to the consumers of this product within the geography of Europe.
category: A:Agriculture, forestry and fishing/01:Crop and animal production, hunting and related service activities/016:Support activities to agriculture and post-harvest crop activities/0161:Support activities for crop production
